Is thy fréedome fettered? Are thy sences besotted?
Is thy witte inueygled? Werte thou of late a defier
of Venus, and arte thou nowe a defender of vanitie.

Diddest thou of late renounce beautie as a foe, and wilt
thou now imbrace her as a friende. Is this the carefull
